## Description {#details}

A range of filename indices.

Used to specify the location of a batch of filenames in a vector-like container.

Definition at line 541 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/profiledata/lib/profiledata/coverage/coveragemappingreader-cpp">CoverageMappingReader.cpp</a>.
